test: I ye mun san sugula wa Bala?
What did Bala buy at the market?
I y'a ye sugula wa Musa Madu?
Did Musa see Madu at the market?
Wari tè Madu fè dè wa?
I kòròke taara min wa Musa?
Ayi, n'man Madu ye sugula kunun.
I taara sugu kònò kunun wa?
Owò. N'taara yen ni n'muso ye.
No, (he/Musa) went to (market/there) with his wife
